{"tid":639830,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"窮人唔好生仔=矛盾","createTime":"2018-04-23T20:00:10.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-23T23:40:01.000Z","uid":58316,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"bff03464936132710a763aaf91490c756abe349c","tid":639830,"uid":58316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T20:00:10.000Z","msg":"真係窮人<br />\n窮到冇得再輸個隻<br />\n話之你死<br />\n最好生十件八件攬炒<br />\n所以你見d難民咁鍾意強姦人<br />\n離鄉別井<br />\n身上一蚊都冇<br />\n橫掂都係等死咪爽下先<br />\n當一個人冇野可以輸<br />\n忽然間<br />\n乜都可以做<br />\n因為根本冇成本<br />\n有自覺而唔生仔既「窮人」<br />\n好似香港基層咁<br />\n窮極有個譜<br />\n有收入有飯食有劏房/公屋住<br />\n放工返屋企睇東張西望<br />\n生左細路連屎都冇得食<br />\n所以話<br />\n識諗既一定唔會係窮人<br />\n窮人又一定唔會理你"},{"pid":"2d88edc2fd82ebc5e797b747e3445a53f622201c","tid":639830,"uid":65858,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T20:08:41.000Z","msg":"所以生仔要考牌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60f8c633c42e46c4e6629856acd531d99673ef6f","tid":639830,"uid":51748,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T20:29:09.000Z","msg":"咪即係類似種族清洗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但係係香港根本唔work<br />\n班友咪又係話要返工 然後做咩都不了<br />\n同埋近年dse少左好多人考 證明d人都傾向唔生/淨係生1個"},{"pid":"f85c3563214ca6f07f6eb9a3cc829c8a44735b70","tid":639830,"uid":155732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"60f8c633c42e46c4e6629856acd531d99673ef6f","tid":639830,"uid":51748,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T20:29:09.000Z","msg":"咪即係類似種族清洗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但係係香港根本唔work<br />\n班友咪又係話要返工 然後做咩都不了<br />\n同埋近年dse少左好多人考 證明d人都傾向唔生/淨係生1個"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T20:31:51.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">咪即係類似種族清洗</span><br />\n歐洲啲左膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad17cf946f0b9cb879fa3df1230b82f9b2ba07bd","tid":639830,"uid":44510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T20:39:42.000Z","msg":"所以新腥港人一黎就生幾件<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n拎間公屋又大啲、綜緩又拎多啲<br />\n一個唔覺意仲有社工跟，仔都唔洗點湊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9d681c74d0a51ee6be1d2e3dc03d66ad9c725e1","tid":639830,"uid":123456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T20:53:19.000Z","msg":"窮人咪生仔<br />\n呢句主要係為左個仔著想姐<br />\n你係都要生姐係唔係為個仔著想，呢句咪唔啱你用<br />\n<br />\n雖然呢句好on9<br />\n你見本土派掉磚嗰啲好多都係窮人<br />\n冇左窮細路呢啲未來支柱<br />\n本土派點算"},{"pid":"77adbbeaac0ecf8f50c7dde5c6c7aef3b1b1f17c","tid":639830,"uid":40470,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T23:40:01.000Z","msg":"MK中出生好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n為未來帶來廉價勞動力<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n連登窮撚既老豆就係D過氣老MK<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}